{"tid":430835,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【自由鬥士】   南亞裔社工 Jeffrey Andrews 為港人出頭","createTime":"2017-10-10T07:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T06:21:30.000Z","uid":82646,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9b2bb9a17a0ebeb5ca58244a161ec0586d99c754","tid":430835,"uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"　Jeffrey Andrews<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/12191663_1079846928701337_7910285618563457549_n.jpg?oh=15fa5bd9987c5c606731b21ff0655420&amp;oe=5A3F1412\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F12191663_1079846928701337_7910285618563457549_n.jpg%3Foh%3D15fa5bd9987c5c606731b21ff0655420%26oe%3D5A3F1412&h=89805196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hongkongfp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/photo6237817257703090130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fphoto6237817257703090130.jpg&h=0026da1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJeffrey Andrews  右三者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_171008/20171008_225912ec223a52ad00a2arvxnj4VlBCD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_171008%2F20171008_225912ec223a52ad00a2arvxnj4VlBCD.jpg&h=1f66182c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南亞裔團體「Voices of Diversity」投訴醫院冇人識&quot;南亞&quot;翻譯員, 未能享有公營醫療服務;  指責本地幼稚園拒絕接收非本地學生，令他們缺乏學習中文的機會，導致       難以融入社會<br />\nJeffrey Andrews  右一者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　Jeffrey Andrews 簡歷 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- 於2002年8月加入黑社會<br />\n<br />\n- 曾參與打鬥、收陀地、偷竊、負責召集人馬<br />\n<br />\n- 曾因搶電話和打架而被警察拘捕<br />\n<br />\n- 2006年 打劫後被警察截查，人贓並獲<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">融樂會</span>前總幹事王惠芬協助<span style=\"color: red;\">保釋</span>, 找來多封求情信<br />\n    , 成功<span style=\"color: red;\">避過入獄及留案底,</span>  只簽保守行為一年<br />\n<br />\n- 於基督教勵行會工作，<span style=\"color: red;\">負責輔導難民</span><br />\n<br />\n- 重慶大廈的服務中心工作<br />\n<br />\n- 2015, 成為社工<br />\n<br />\n- 2017,  南亞團體「Voices of Diversity」到政府總部外遞交請願信<br />\n             Jeff 指責本地幼稚園拒絕接收非本地學生，令他們缺乏學習中文的機會，導致       難以融入社會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Jeffery說:   他選擇繼續做難民服務。自己的角色一方面是<span style=\"color: red;\">協助難民</span>，同時亦<span style=\"color: red;\">希望教育香港人<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/922877/922877_20170213-131542.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2F922877%2F922877_20170213-131542.png&h=304b1faa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://www.symedialab.org.hk/talk/%E4%B8%89%E5%8D%81%E8%80%8C%E7%AB%8B-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A6%96%E5%90%8D%E5%8D%B0%E8%A3%94%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.symedialab.org.hk%2Ftalk%2F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%258D%2581%25E8%2580%258C%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%258D%25B0%25E8%25A3%2594%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5%2F&d=kz8aiBPLgMO%2BSHg0%2B83J0bZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=aac977bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.symedialab.org.hk/talk/%E4%B8%89%E5%8D%81%E8%80%8C%E7%AB%8B-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A6%96%E5%90%8D%E5%8D%B0%E8%A3%94%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%BF%E5%BF%83%E6%9C%88%E5%88%8A/%E5%BE%9E%E7%8A%AF%E4%BA%8B%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%B0%E9%A6%96%E4%BD%8D%E5%8D%B0%E8%A3%94%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5-jeffrey-andrews/1077512665601430/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2588%258A%2F%25E5%25BE%259E%25E7%258A%25AF%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2588%25B0%25E9%25A6%2596%25E4%25BD%258D%25E5%258D%25B0%25E8%25A3%2594%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5-jeffrey-andrews%2F1077512665601430%2F&d=kz